Package: scrutr
Title: A Toolkit for Structured Datasets Exploitation
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R:
    person("Daniel", "Rakotomalala", , "rakdanielh@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A set of functions for exploiting collections of structured
    datasets (data frames) at scale. Core capabilities include batch
    inspection and profiling, variable presence detection across datasets,
    type consistency checking, format conversion, and file management
    helpers. Designed for workflows involving multiple related datasets
    with a common structure.
